OL,7,FThe investigation by Jacqueline Perry
OL,8,FKC was launched by Reform UK after
OL,9,Fthey received complaints from two
OL,10,Fwomen working in Lowe's offices, who
OL,11,Fcomplained of bullying and
OL,12,Funacceptable conduct from men in the
OL,13,Fteam.
OL,15,FIn her report, Perry concludes: "There
OL,16,Fis veracity in the complaints from
OL,17,Fboth women which amounts 'credible
OL,18,Fevidence'".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
