OL,7,FShe writes that Lowe failed to
OL,8,F"address the alleged toxic conduct" of
OL,9,Fmale colleagues in the office, and
OL,10,Fsays he did not take the allegations
OL,11,Fseriously.
OL,13,F"At the very least Mr Lowe should have
OL,14,Ftaken seriously the distress and
OL,15,Fconcerns of a seasoned Parliamentary
OL,16,Femployee and of both women", Perry
OL,17,Fsays.
