OL,7,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,8,FPolitics? Tom, Robert and Anushka dig
OL,9,Finto the biggest issues dominating the
OL,10,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,12,FShe writes that Lowe had a "duty and
OL,13,Fresponsibility to ensure systems were
OL,14,Fin place to avoid junior members of
OL,15,Fstaff being treated in any unfair and
OL,16,Fdiscriminatory way", and said there's
OL,17,Fa "real risk" that the
OL,18,F"discrimination" in the office could
OL,19,Fbe a breach of the Equality Act.
