OL,7,FIn response to the report, Lowe
OL,8,Finsists the claims are "outright lies"
OL,9,Fand called the process "disgustingly
OL,10,Fbiased".
OL,12,FIn a post on X, the Independent MP
OL,13,Fsaid "Reform is shamefully attacking
OL,14,Fmy innocent staff to smear my name",
OL,15,Finsisting Reform only began
OL,16,Finvestigating the complaints after he
OL,17,Fpublicly criticised leader Nigel
OL,18,FFarage in the Daily Mail.
