OL,7,FThe report details some of the
OL,8,Faccusations and incidents described by
OL,9,Fthe two women - one said she
OL,10,Fcomplained to Lowe after being
OL,11,F"constantly criticised" by another
OL,12,Fmale staff member. She says Lowe was
OL,13,F"dismissive" of the claims, and made
OL,14,Fclear "he was not afraid to get rid of
OL,15,Fanyone".
OL,17,FThe woman says she was then "frozen
OL,18,Fout" by Lowe, and subsequently signed
OL,19,Foff work by her doctor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
