OL,7,FThe bitter row broke out between Lowe
OL,8,Fand Farage earlier this month, after
OL,9,Fthe two clashed over the claims about
OL,10,FLowe's behaviour and Farage's
OL,11,Fleadership.
OL,13,FTensions between Lowe and Farage
OL,14,Fappeared to have been brewing for some
OL,15,Fmonths, with Farage disagreeing with
OL,16,Fsome of Lowe's more extreme language
OL,17,Fand views.
